---

## 🧠 Overview  

**Maria** is a voice-based conversational AI agent built with **Vapi.ai** for **XYZ Bank**.  
She acts as an empathetic collections representative, helping customers handle overdue payments through natural, respectful, and context-aware dialogue.  

This project was developed as part of a **Prompt Engineering assignment**, focusing on tone design, verification logic, and human-like conversational flow.

---

## ✨ Features  

- 🔐 **Identity Verification** — Validates users by DOB or last 4 digits of SSN.  
- 💳 **Debt & Payment Handling** — Explains overdue amounts and offers flexible plans.  
- 🧠 **Human-Like Conversations** — Short, natural, and emotionally intelligent.  
- ⚡ **Real-Time Voice** — Powered by **Vapi WebSockets** for low-latency dialogue.  
- 🌍 **Multilingual** — Supports multiple Indian languages.  
- 🛡️ **Compliance Guardrails** — Prevents hallucinations and ensures accurate disclosures.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack  

| Component | Provider | Role |
|------------|-----------|------|
| **Vapi.ai** | — | Voice agent orchestration |
| **Deepgram Nova-2** | Speech-to-Text | Real-time transcription |
| **OpenAI GPT-4o mini** | LLM | Core reasoning and dialogue |
| **ElevenLabs TurboV2.5** | TTS | Human-like voice synthesis |
| **Node.js / APIs** | (Planned) | Banking data integration |

